Review_body:
Story-line => 3/5 (The story-line was predictable and got many loose ends.);
Acting => 3/5 (Most of the character's acting was terrible.);
Directing => 2/5 (Directing was so bad that I got bored in the middle.);
Visual Effects/Animation => 4/5 (Considering 1982, it's pretty good. But the previous one was better.);
Screenplay => 3/5 (I think this is the part where everything got lost.);
Personal Recommendation => 3/5 (Don't watch it if you're not a Star Trek fan);
Most Favorite Character => Spock (Amidst all the mess, he was the only character who made the movie worth something to be watched.);
